Package: advligorts-daqd
Architecture: any
Depends:
 advligorts-mbuf-dkms,
 advligorts-symmetricom-dkms,
 mx,
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: advLigoRTS daqd binaries
 Core component of advLigoRTS.
 .
 This package installs all daqd components:
  * daqd_dc_mx: data concentrator
  * daqd_bcst: frame broadcaster
  * daqd_fw: frame writer
  * daqd_rcv: NDS1 server
  * daqd_mxsymm: all-in-one mx receiver systems
  * daqd_standiop: daqd for stand-alone systems
  * nds: archive data retriever for NDS1

